00:54:08.510 --> 00:54:13.510
It is situated on a narrow slice of land surrounded by the sea.

00:54:13.510 --> 00:54:19.510
Katas has a wealth of vistas and well-preserved historical landmarks.

00:54:20.510 --> 00:54:24.510
On the outskirts lies Puerto de Santa Maria,

00:54:24.510 --> 00:54:27.510
where in English-speaking congregation meets.

00:54:27.510 --> 00:54:33.510
