00:54:36.510 --> 00:54:42.510
as well as distant lands such as Australia, Britain, Canada and the United States.

00:54:42.510 --> 00:54:48.510
Katas has a high rate of unemployment, so finding work is not easy.

00:54:48.510 --> 00:54:56.510
One couple travels nearly 300 miles or 483 kilometers every Thursday to their territory

00:54:56.510 --> 00:55:01.510
